## Task 1 {.scrollable}

1.  A mistake happened during data entry for sample id 16. Use `mutate()` and `case_when()` to change the ts value of 0.72 to 8.72.



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sludge |> 
    mutate(ts = case_when(
        ts ==  0.72 ~ 8.72,
        .default = ts
    ))
```
:::

